Bard Offshore’s Potential Buyers Are From U.S., Asia, FTD Reports

-- B y   S h e e n a g h   M a t t h e w s
-- 
2011-09-06T05:53:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-06/bard-offshore-s-potential-buyers-are-from-u-s-asia-ftd-says.html
General Electric Co. (GE)  may be
interested in buying German offshore wind-farm builder Bard
Holding GmbH,  Financial Times Deutschland said , citing people
from the industry it didn’t name.  Bard Offshore, which is seeking a buyer for the 87 percent
formerly held by company founder Arngolt Bekker, has received
inquiries from potential buyers in  Asia  and the U.S. and expects
to agree on a sale by the first quarter of next year, the German
newspaper said, citing an interview with Chief Executive Officer
Bernd Ranneberg.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sheenagh Matthews in Frankfurt at 
 smatthews6@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Benedikt Kammel at 
 bkammel@bloomberg.net  